  "commit_message": "fix(eslint-plugin): use version ranges for typescript-eslint deps\n\n@endo/eslint-plugin is a published package, so exact pins in its\ndependencies are contagious: they force every downstream consumer onto\nexactly 8.39.1, preventing deduplication and producing peer-dependency\nconflicts (e.g. tooling requesting @typescript-eslint/utils ^8.56.0).\n\nThese were pinned to exact 8.39.1 in 58ef1d9ec (\"lint: stabilize pack\ntypechecks ...\", PR #2327 \"use Yarn's pnpm linker\") to keep the\ntypescript-eslint fam",
